                <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Victor b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> l<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>eg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Itali</abbr><ex>cae</ex></expan> vixit annis X<supplied reason="lost">XXVIII</supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>itavit</ex></expan> annis XVIII <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Se<supplied reason="lost">veri</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>anus <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> Durosteri <note>sic</note> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">fra</supplied>tri dulcissimo posui<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Αἴλιος Βίκτωρ, β(ενε)φ(ικιάριος) ὑπατικοῦ λεγ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/>ῶνος πρώτης Ἰταλικῆς, ἔζησε <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">ἔ</supplied>τη λη, ἐστρατεύσατο ἔτη ιη, <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Α</supplied>ἴλιος Σεουηριανὸς βουλεύτης <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">Δουρ</supplied>οστορησίων, ἀδελφῷ γλυ<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">κυτά</supplied>τῳ ἀνέθηκε.
            </ab></div></div>
